        <div class="service-card-icon">🌐</div>
        <h3>IoT Development</h3>
        <p>Integrate smart devices and advanced technologies to create connected solutions that transform your business operations with our IoT development services.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CASE STUDIES -->
  <section class="tech-case-studies">
    <div class="case-studies-top">
      <h2>Over 600 Projects Delivered Successfully</h2>
      <a href="/our-clients/">See all clients →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="case-studies-main">
      <div class="case-study-featured">
        <img src="https://demskigroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Biopac-1-e1744133149662.png" alt="Biopac" />
        <p>The Demski Group successfully delivered a scalable and efficient web application for Biopac, enabling users to perform and track scientific studies online.</p>
        <a href="/our-clients/biopac/">Read full case study →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="case-studies-grid">
        <div class="case-study-mini">
          <img src="https://demskigroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/ShopOrthopedics-1.png" alt="ShopOrthopedics" />
          <a href="/our-clients/shop-orthopedics/">Read full case study →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="case-study-mini">
          <img src="https://demskigroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/PropertyGauge.png" alt="PropertyGauge" />
          <a href="/our-clients/property-gauge/">Read full case study →</a>
        </div>
